item.title: Liberatersps (The Future Is Now) Join Today!
item.dc:creator: @Nerdypker123 Nerdypker123
item.description:
@Nerdypker123 wrote:

[size=14pt]HOLY SHIT BALLS! You weren’t kidding when you said the future is NOW! I’ve been sitting here since November 04, 2015, 07:01:22 pm, thinking all about how you said this miraculous brain fudgeer. And it has destroyed me. I haven’t been to work in 3 whole days and my boss kept calling but I never answered because I was contemplating life for this amazing future being now brain shitter. My brain has a full poopy pants now, because I started thinking, time is all in our heads! It’s all a ruse. But I’d have to give the server a 0 poopy pants out of 5 because like wimstr said[/size] [quote=“wimstr, post:2, topic:553744”]Seen the same media before, leech?[/quote]
[size=14pt]This media has been used before, and I only remember because of the replies to their media how overly editted it is. Sorry guise. Gotta try harder if you’re gonna leech.[/size]
